<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="47">Megachile patellimana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been recorded from flowers of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Apocynaceae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Apocynaceae</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Apocynaceae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Asclepiadoideae">Asclepiadoideae</taxonomicName>
