<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="47">
In Namibia this species has been recorded from flowers of 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Zygophyllaceae" genus="Crotalaria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Crotalaria podocarpa" order="Geraniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="47" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="podocarpa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="47">Crotalaria podocarpa</emphasis>
